What is JavaScript?
JavaScript is a programming language used primarily by Web browsers to create a dynamic and interactive wepages
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Variables and Types:
-->Global variable-var
-->Local variable-let
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Declare a variable named userAge and assign it a numerical value representing someone's age.
let userage=25;
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Declare another variable named userName and assign it a string value representing a person's name.
let username=" Raj "
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Output both variables using console.log().
console.log(userage);
console.log(username);
